      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver benchmark results for canonical internal flow cases available from vendor documentation.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent benchmark suite includes Couette flow, lid-driven cavity, and pipe flow cases with published order-of-accuracy results. Vendor-supplied verification documentation reviewed and found satisfactory for MRL 2."
