      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index QoI less than 10% across operating points.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (1.8M, 5.2M, 14.6M cells). GCI computed per Celik et al. (2008) protocol. Maximum GCI for normalized hemolysis index was 6.3% at the highest-shear operating point, satisfying the 10% threshold. Medium mesh (5.2M cells) selected for production runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
