      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry and operating conditions span the design space of the COU pump variants.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which shares impeller topology with the COU device family. Operating points in validation bracket the worst-case COU conditions. Fluid properties are representative of clinical blood analog. Validation activities deemed sufficiently relevant for MRL 2 COU."
    },
