      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for rotary blood pump flows (Fraser et al., 2011; Hariharan et al., 2011). Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) is standard for regulatory submissions. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2."
    },
