      "rationale": "Fluid density (1056 kg/m3) and viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s) sourced from published blood analog characterization. Rotational speed and flow boundary conditions taken directly from experimental test matrix. Input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
