    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. Discretization error GCI of 6.3% and NIH prediction error of 14.7% are within acceptance thresholds. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device family under the stated COU.",
